Cauliflower Burger

35 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEgg

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow CarbGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyComfort Food

Description

A delicious, hearty cauliflower burger that satisfies your cravings while being light and nutritious.

Ingredients

  • cauliflower florets: 2 cups
  • breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • grated parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce leaves: 2
  • tomato slices: 1
